extends ../skeleton
block breadcrumb
  li
    a(href='/book-club') Book club
block content
  .grid-row
    .column-two-thirds
      h1.heading-xlarge Book club
      p.lede.
        We need to decide on a book to read.
        There are lots of books in the world, but only some are worth reading.
        We need to narrow them down.

      p.font-small There are three stages to selecting a book.
      p.font-small
        ol.list
          li Creating the longlist
          li Voting on the longlist
          li Voting on the shortlist
      p.font-small We are currently on stage one of three.
      a(href='/book-club/long-list').button.button-start Begin creating the long list
